---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken and Orecchiette with Caramelized Bell Pepper and Parmesan Cream Sauce
description: We think orecciette (“small ears” in Italian!) make the perfect vehicle for a creamy, cheesy sauce like this one. To offset all that richness, we’ve loaded up this dish with plenty of veggies. Spiced up with a little chili pepper heat, this pasta is bound to please!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/565892a3f8b25ed4488b4567.jpg
